data.description: Welcome to your new home sitting on almost an acre lot located on the best street in Madison with a picturesque view and access to the Cumberland River. You will enjoy breathtaking views, beautiful sunsets and a serene atmosphere while sitting on your covered patio or sitting on the covered porch just outside of the master bedroom.  Lots of room for entertaining family and friends. As an added plus, you will find steps that lead you to the banks of the river.  A great fishing spot for those fishermen.  This home features 3 bedrooms and 3 1/2 baths with a flex room for an office, workout area or an additional bedroom. Home was taken down to studs in 2010 and completely renovated.  This home is a perfect blend of comfort and relaxation and a short drive to downtown Nashville. Don't miss this rare find located on the Cumberland River.
